data.description: Will not last, beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath pool home! This beautiful home located in Ashley Oaks in Riverview, with new HVAC. The lush mature landscaping greats you as you pull into the driveway and walk up to the door. As you walk in you will see to the right a formal dining room, in front of you a great room, with French doors that lead to the patio and pool. To the left, you will find a master suite, which boasts upgraded paint, beautiful flooring, and double doors to the pool/patio area outside. Follow past the right and left side closets into the upgraded bath with dual sinks and medicine closets. Off the master bath, is a secondary bedroom with floor-to-ceiling bookshelves and closet. As you enter the kitchen you find stainless steel appliances, upgraded granite, lighting, and gorgeous cabinetry. The open space includes a nook space and a family room with double doors, and tons of windows for natural light! To the left, you will find 2 great size bedrooms and a full bath. Outside one of the three sets of doors, you will find a great space for entertaining! The lanai wraps around the large pool, with 2 ways in, and gives the most space for having fun! Welcome Home!!
